{"title":"奶牛的锻炼","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2161","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>奶牛Bessie有N分钟时间跑步，每分钟她可以跑步或者休息。若她在第i分钟跑步，可以跑出D_i米，同时疲倦程度增加1（初始为0）。若她在第i分钟休息，则疲倦程度减少1。无论何时，疲倦程度都不能超过M。另外，一旦她开始休息，只有当疲惫程度减为0时才能重新开始跑步。在第N分钟后，她的疲倦程度必须为0。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行，两个整数，代表N和M。<br>接下来N行，每行一个整数，代表D_i。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>Bessie想知道，她最多能跑的距离。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5 2<br>5<br>3<br>4<br>2<br>10</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>9</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N &lt;= 2000 , M &lt;= 500 , D_i &lt;= 1000</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}